            {
               "text": "<p><span id=\"htZoomImageMsg\"></span></p><p><span id=\"htAmericaAbyaYalaMsg\"></span> (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('160fb48c-1711-491e-a1aa-e1257e7889af'); return false;\">Porto-Gonçalves, Carlos Walter, <htdate0>, pp. 39-43</a>).</p><p><i>This text is part of the \"<b>The Discoverer(s)</b>\" stage of the <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('96f3d3af-15c3-4c37-9d0e-e4b7db0db1db'); return false;\">Scientific Method</a> game by History Tracers. We recommend that readers play at least this stage to observe the practical application of the method.</i></p>",
