               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text discusses different paths taken by human beings on their way to the American continent (*Abya Yala*). For better understanding, we suggest reviewing the sections *First Steps*, *Understanding Texts* and *Atlas* (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>).",
