            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img class=\"imgcenter\" src=\"images/Archive/BRes140146_0206.jpg\" /><b>Figure 1</b>: Excerpt from the letter written by Christopher Columbus, where he reports the discovery of the route to the Indies (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('6bffd681-8f79-4773-914b-45fcc09bb6a2'); return false;\">Cristóbal Colon, <htdate0>, pp. 185</a>).</p>",
