            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img class=\"imgcenter\" src=\"images/UNESCO/Lanse.jpg\" /><b>Figure 2</b>: National archaeological site L’Anse aux Meadows. Photo by Dick Houghtton, published by UNESCO (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('35411d10-e127-42ab-b1c9-13b4461e4ea8'); return false;\">UNESCO, <htdate0></a>). Shared under license <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/2.0/deed.en\" target=\"_blank\">Attribution-Noncommercial 2.0 Generic</a>.</p>",
