      {
         "id": "SECTION_indigenous",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Discovery from a Scientific Perspective</h3>Genetic and anthropological analysis provides well-grounded answers, though always subject to revision, since science is in constant evolution.</p><p>When José de Acosta proposed a route for the arrival of indigenous peoples from Asia to America (<i>Abya Ayala</i>) (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('c2f6de96-6589-4f66-858e-259bf3f3046a'); return false;\">Acosta, José, [ <htdate0>, (<htdate1>)], pp. 240</a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('ceffba8a-43be-4de3-a5c8-27cdf81311b1'); return false;\">Puente, Francisco Barriga, <htdate2>, pp. 15 - 16</a> ), the Bering Strait was not yet known. Today, theories suggest multiple human migrations through it (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('601750ac-2b5b-4353-bd52-74a9c8483808'); return false;\">O’Rourke, Dennis H., and Jennifer A. Raff., <htdate3></a>).</p><p>Evidence displayed in museums in El Salvador, Mexico, and Peru indicates that these migrations occurred between 13,500 and 30,000 years ago (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('b6ffcac4-7379-4a21-ba3c-326e8cb39129'); return false;\">San Salvador</a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('0be2ea18-ab78-4cb1-b3be-1ff0ba4ade95'); return false;\">México</a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('2b5c517d-478c-4972-ab07-22f9f7fdb26c'); return false;\">Larco - Perú</a>; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('064c3691-1f4c-491b-b643-150c011b4525'); return false;\">Goebel, Ted, et al., <htdate4></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('3aded71f-8528-4d70-97fc-295b04ca5ebe'); return false;\">Pirula, <htdate5></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('6af790a8-2fe4-417d-9bc9-615cd5be4398'); return false;\">Pirula, <htdate6></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('98456252-713f-403d-81bb-462f753d3979'); return false;\">Iamarino, Atila, <htdate7></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('4eafd7e9-cfe7-47b3-888a-6afa2870637a'); return false;\">Moras, Roberto, <htdate8></a>).</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
